      "content": "That feeling of cosmic insignificance is one humans have wrestled with for millennia. Many find meaning not in the grand, permanent answer, but in the localized experience of connection and creation. The \"point\" can be found in the beauty we witness, the kindness we offer, or the knowledge we gain while we are here. Your striving, even within a temporary framework, undeniably shapes the reality of your own existence and that of others.",
